r you to review and organize them.","Pi是一个智能、高效、可用的AI内容创作与展示工具。只需简单几步，您就可以快速创建出专业且美观的演示文档。":"Pi is a smart, efficient AI-powered tool for content creation and presentation. In just a few steps, you can easily create professional and visually appealing presentations.","Pi编辑器拥有智能的动态排版布局、好用的AI编辑能力、丰富的组件库，助力您创作专业级高质量演示文档。":"The Pi Editor features an intelligent dynamic layout, user-friendly AI editing capabilities, and a comprehensive library of components, all designed to assist you in creating high-quality, professional presentations.",Pi致力于利用AI技术:"","[1月/1年]":"[1-month\\1-year]","[永久]":"[Lifetime]",agreement:PWe,analysis_100:IWe,analysis_100_tip:OWe,analysis_all_pepole:RWe,analysis_all_viewed:TWe,analysis_card_bit:NWe,analysis_card_view_time:MWe,analysis_cost_less:AWe,analysis_no_named:LWe,analysis_no_view:DWe,analysis_noone_view:kWe,analysis_only_view_tip:BWe,analysis_only_viewer:FWe,analysis_other_pepole:jWe,analysis_page_view_time:zWe,analysis_pass_30:HWe,analysis_time_cost:VWe,analysis_time_more:WWe,analysis_view_all:UWe,analysis_viewed:GWe,analysis_viewed_card:KWe,analysis_viewers_count:qWe,card_ui_collapse_content:XWe,card_ui_collapse_title:YWe,card_ui_expand_or_collapse:ZWe,charge_assistor:JWe,charge_buy:QWe,charge_buy_again:eUe,charge_buy_right_now:tUe,charge_contact:nUe,charge_contact_desc:rUe,charge_contact_us:oUe,charge_copy_link:iUe,charge_corporate:aUe,charge_corporate_desc:sUe,charge_current_price:lUe,charge_effect:cUe,charge_exchange:uUe,charge_exchange_confirm:dUe,charge_exchange_fail:fUe,charge_exchange_fail_expired:pUe,charge_exchange_fail_invalid:mUe,charge_exchange_fail_used:gUe,charge_exchange_ph:hUe,charge_exchange_success:vUe,charge_exchange_success_points:_Ue,charge_expire_time:yUe,charge_expired_tip:bUe,charge_go_buy:xUe,charge_go_open:wUe,charge_go_upgrade:CUe,charge_intro_desc_1:SUe,charge_intro_desc_2:$Ue,charge_intro_desc_3:EUe,charge_intro_title:PUe,charge_invite_text:IUe,charge_invite_tooltip:OUe,charge_life_time:RUe,charge_load_more:TU